<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Lagrangian_mechanics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Lev_Landau" title="Lev Landau">Landau, L.D.</a> and <a href="/wiki/Evgeny_Lifshitz" title="Evgeny Lifshitz">Lifshitz, E.M.</a> <i>Mechanics</i>, Pergamon Press.</li>
<li>Gupta, Kiran Chandra, <i>Classical mechanics of particles and rigid bodies</i> (Wiley, 1988).</li>
</ul>
